{"tid":2246236,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【召喚大和田】美國升級核武庫   中国必須確保自身核威懾","createTime":"2020-10-17T01:32:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T13:07:59.000Z","uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bdebe8825e698b0ada92db36748fd158b626be39","tid":2246236,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T01:32:08.000Z","msg":"外交部：美國升級核武庫 中國須對核力量規模保持適度模糊<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部軍控司司長傅聰表示，中國始終恪守在任何時候和任何情況下不首先使用核武器，對成為核超級大國不感興趣。惟當前美國正持續昇級其龐大核武庫，奉行進攻性的核戰略，對中國核力量的生存性造成衝擊，在此背景下，中國必須對核力量規模保持適度模糊，以確保自身核威懾的有效性。如美願將自身核力量降至中國水平，中國願參與國際核裁軍談判，但這在可預見的將來恐怕不會發生。<br />\n<br />\n傅聰指，中國奉行自衛防禦的最低核威懾戰略，是基於中國自身安全需要和核武器作為終極威懾手段的性質等考量作出的戰略選擇，外界對中國核武器數量的猜測毫無根據。中方加強戰略能力建設，是新形勢下確保核武庫安全性和可靠性的客觀需要，希望外界客觀正確看待。<br />\n<br />\n傅聰指出，美國提出所謂的三邊軍控談判，是為其自身擺脫條約束縛製造藉口。中國核力量與美俄相比完全不在一個量級，要求中國參加所謂的三邊軍控談判不公平、不合理、不可行，中國不會參加。但這不意味著迴避自身核裁軍責任，中國願意在聯合國、裁談會和五核國機制等框架下，與各方探討事關戰略穩定的廣泛問題，也願在相互尊重基礎上與各方就戰略安全問題開展雙邊對話，但不接受任何脅迫與訛詐。"},{"pid":"07ebaa3baa6e1d7bd6d8dd60096fc716463fd2af","tid":2246236,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T01:32:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/chi/1899719/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fchi%2F1899719%2F&d=6FpmejEDNbHOA1ae24hao4Mqd%2FJDLPQOR3COl2rYgn0%3D&h=4ecf98ce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fchi%2F1899719%2F&h=db978d37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/chi/1899719/</a>"},{"pid":"505f4afa8e7138290cb53ed693ed21482e5b074e","tid":2246236,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T01:33:26.000Z","msg":"召喚大和田常務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0ab07df7610ab8cbe577aeaa92b8887c79d32b3","tid":2246236,"uid":61653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T01:34:55.000Z","msg":"支那啲火箭飛都飛唔起俾多幾廿粒彈頭佢都係原地爆啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afe0e6d48d0758fb332365c8ba27bc6e64a54c61","tid":2246236,"uid":168998,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T01:38:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Acz0FAD.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAcz0FAD.gif&h=426e1bba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"762653ac2cd506ea43037adfea094152e755f2e3","tid":2246236,"uid":12757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"505f4afa8e7138290cb53ed693ed21482e5b074e","tid":2246236,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T01:33:26.000Z","msg":"召喚大和田常務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T13:07:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/DimwittedBronzeChrysomelid-size_restricted.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FDimwittedBronzeChrysomelid-size_restricted.gif&h=ad773399&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}